703737f-a.title: Brooklyn: Columbia Street - Nelson Street
703737f-a.text:
111
Columbia Street, east side, north from Nelson Street.
The point of vantage is Dwight Street, which meets Columbia
Street at this point. The four-story house is at the S. E.
oorner of Luqueer Street.
October 21, 1939
P. L. Sperr
12:
The sast side of Columbia Street, south from Luqueer
to Nelson Streets. The four-story house is the same as the
one in View 1.
October 21, 1939
P. L. Sperr
